List the required knowledge/skills of a job profile in a readable format.
!!!
SELECT ks.title || ' (' || ks.skill_level || ' level) ' || ks.description
FROM jp_ks jpks
LEFT OUTER JOIN knowledge_skill ks ON jpks.ks_code = ks.ks_code
WHERE jpks.job_code = ?
!!!
1
!!!
1
!!!
Choose a job_code:
!!!
select job_code from jp_ks
!!!
1
!!!
